				<p>Ayant une formation Web, je possede une base en HTML, Bootstrap, CSS, TypeScript, JavaScript,
					<br>
					PHP, Figma, Node JS, Mongodb, Laragon</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row d-flex justify-content-between">
				<div class="col-md-5">
					<p>HTML / TWIG / BOOTSTRAP</p>
					<div class="progress mb-4" style="height: 20px">
